graph TD
    A[User Question] --> B{Agentic LLM Core}
    
    subgraph Reasoning Loop
    B -->|Thought: Do I need internal data?| C{Decision}
    C -->|Yes: I need policy info| D[Execute Retriever Tool]
    C -->|Yes: I need live data| E[Execute Web Search Tool]
    C -->|No: Standard Query| F[Generate Native Answer]
    end
    
    subgraph RAG Integration
    D -->|Query Vector Database| G[(Knowledge Base)]
    G -->|Returns Docs + Metadata| D
    D -->|Inject Docs into Context| B
    end
    
    B -->|Final Synthesis| H[Structured Output]
    H --> I[Response with Citations]
